Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Contact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDisplayable

    public class Contact
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDisplayable
    Builds a contact class which implements the IDisplayable interface It provides information Such as name, phone number, email, date and contact type for every new contact registered.
